::Battera::

She emerged from the CR chamber fully repaired.  She transformed into bat 
mode and stretched her wings.  She felt great.  She needed the CR chamber 
more than she realized.  She transformed back into bot mode. She looked to 
see if Cybershark was still there or not.  She wanted to thank him before 
she left. She knew she had to get out of there as soon as possable.  She 
didn't want them to capture her and kill her like her friends. Her friends, 
she thought, they must be dead by now.  HellBeast surely has killed them. 
She mumbled something about how she left them when they needed her.  She sat 
down in front of the CR chamber and covered her eyes trying to blot out the 
memory from her mind.
